pullRequest.bodyText:
This PR contains following changes:

internal binding event system has been refactored: now each event has its own handler method; this way there is no need to check type of incoming event in handlers;
basic response validation has been moved to base class SatelCommandBase;
handleResponse has been splitted to avoid necessity of calling super class handleResponse;
workaround for https://community.openhab.org/t/satel-zones-not-work/91620/15 in SatelModule has been added - it ignores responses that don't match sent command;

Signed-off-by: Krzysztof Goworek krzysztof.goworek@gmail.com

